Package com.i2group.apollo.model.schema

Contains enumerations that enable you to identify system-defined item and property types programmatically, and interfaces that provide domain-specific representations of geospatial values.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IGeospatialSourceData A geospatial location represented in its source data form.
IGeospatialValue A fully defined geospatial location.
ISpatialReferenceAndValue A geospatial location represented in machine-readable form.
IWGS84Value A geospatial location represented in the WGS84 system.
 

Enum Summary
AlertFeedPropertyTypeId Provides a way to look up the property group type identifiers and property type identifiers for the system-defined item type named "Alert Feed".
AlertSubscriptionPropertyTypeId Provides a way to look up the property group type identifiers and property type identifiers for the system-defined item type named "Alert Feed Subscription".
ChartPropertyTypeId Provides a way to look up the property type identifiers for the system-defined item type named "Analyst's Notebook Chart".
SetPropertyTypeId Provides a way to look up the property type identifiers for the system-defined item type named "Set".
StoredQueryPropertyTypeId Provides a way to look up the property group type identifiers and property type identifiers for the system-defined item type named "Stored Query".
SystemType Indicates the type of an item that has one of the system types in the schema.
UserPropertyTypeId Provides a way to look up the property type identifiers for the system-defined item type named "User".
 

Package com.i2group.apollo.model.schema Description

Contains enumerations that enable you to identify system-defined item and property types programmatically, and interfaces that provide domain-specific representations of geospatial values.
